== Mobile Patient Demographics Query [ITI-78] ==
activate PDC1
PDC1 ->> SupplierFacade : 
deactivate PDC1
activate SupplierFacade
note right of SupplierFacade: Internal processing
dashed line -[hidden]-> ConsumerFacade
activate ConsumerFacade
group  Patient Demographics \nQuery [ITI-21]\nor Patient Demographics \nQuery for HL7v3 [ITI-47]
